---
import PortalShell from "../layouts/PortalShell.astro";
---

<PortalShell activePage="market" title="商城" description="FreedomPost 的服务与资源入口。">
  <header class="page-hero portal-container">
    <p class="eyebrow"><span></span> Market</p>
    <div class="page-hero-row"><div><h1>商城</h1><p>服务、资源和数字内容将以独立商品的形式在这里展示。</p></div></div>
  </header>
  <section class="portal-section market-section">
    <div class="portal-container market-layout">
      <div class="market-intro"><p class="section-kicker">Storefront</p><h2>独立路由已经就绪</h2><p>商城不会混在首页或文章页面中。商品、库存、下单和支付将在后续接入独立的数据模型与订单流程后开放。</p></div>
      <div class="market-placeholder" aria-label="商城状态"><i data-lucide="store"></i><strong>商城准备中</strong><span>当前不提供购买入口，避免展示无法完成的订单流程。</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PortalShell>
